Commentary Text: Bhuvneshwar to Abhinav Manohar, out Caught by Tripathi!! And finally a catch has been taken! Abhinav Manohar goes for another flat batted slap against this short ball and gets a top-edge straight down the ground. Tripathi from long-off sprints across, keeps his eyes on the ball and takes an impressive catch. Dropped a sitter earlier in the over, but takes a difficult chance this time around.
